functions.name: run_mypy
functions.docstring:
Clears the cache and run mypy before running any of the typing tests.

The mypy results are cached in `OUTPUT_MYPY` for further use.

The cache refresh can be skipped using

NUMPY_TYPING_TEST_CLEAR_CACHE=0 pytest numpy/typing/tests

functions.name: test_reveal
functions.docstring:
Validate that mypy correctly infers the return-types of
the expressions in `path`.

functions.name: test_code_runs
functions.docstring: Validate that the code in `path` properly during runtime.
